      "title": "Rock falls on many roads in the mountains",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "On the Nortonbridge main road, in Hapugasthana post 05 area and in Diyagala area, the traffic movement on the road was blocked for several hours due to the collapse of mounds and stones on the road this morning.",
        "These mounds have collapsed with the heavy rains falling in the area."
      ],
